  <brief_title>Treatment of Androgenetic Alopecia in Females, 9 Beam</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of the HairMax LaserComb 2009, 9 Beam Model: For the Treatment of Androgenetic Alopecia in Females</official_title>
