          <description>This arm involves the active LLLT device with 9 laser modules. The device is used 3 times a week for 12 minutes per session for full 26 duration of the study. This device was distributed to subjects in a blinded randomized manner. Subjects were evaluated at 8, 16 and 26 weeks, with hair counts performed at week 16 and 26.</description>
